<script type="text/javascript"> var root = document.getElementsByTagName( "html" )[0]; root.setAttribute( "class", "js" ); </script><script>
(function() {

    setTimeout(() => {

        console.log('Updating Script Infinite Scroll Script to prepend /blog to paging requests');

        function anchovy_custom_request( url, responseType, onLoad, onError, onLast ) {
        var req = new XMLHttpRequest();
        req.open( 'GET', url, true );
        // set responseType document to return DOM
        req.responseType = responseType || '';

        // set X-Requested-With header to check that is ajax request
        req.setRequestHeader('X-Requested-With', 'XMLHttpRequest');

        req.onload = function() {
            if ( req.status == 200 ) {
            onLoad( req.response );
            } else if ( req.status == 204 ) {
            onLast( req.response );
            } else {
            // not 200 OK, error
            var error = new Error( req.statusText );
            onError( error );
            }
        };

        // Handle network errors
        req.onerror = function() {
            var error = new Error( 'Network error requesting ' + url );
            onError( error );
        };

        req.send();
        }

        InfiniteScroll.prototype.loadNextPage = function() {
        if ( this.isLoading || !this.canLoad ) {
            return;
        }

        var path = this.getAbsolutePath();
        path = '/blog' + path;
        this.isLoading = true;

        var onLoad = function( response ) {
            this.onPageLoad( response, path );
        }.bind( this );

        var onError = function( error ) {
            this.onPageError( error, path );
        }.bind( this );

        var onLast = function( response ) {
            this.lastPageReached( response, path );
        }.bind( this );

        anchovy_custom_request( path, this.options.responseType, onLoad, onError, onLast );
        this.dispatchEvent( 'request', null, [ path ] );
        };
    }, 1000)
})();
</script><meta name="generator" content="Powered by WPBakery Page Builder - drag and drop page builder for WordPress."/>

		<div id="fws_654ab41b1cfb3"  data-column-margin="default" data-midnight="light" data-top-percent="7%" data-bottom-percent="7%"  class="wpb_row vc_row-fluid vc_row top-level full-width-section  vc_row-o-equal-height vc_row-flex  vc_row-o-content-bottom standard_section "  style="padding-top: calc(100vw * 0.07); padding-bottom: calc(100vw * 0.07); "><div class="row-bg-wrap" data-bg-animation="none" data-bg-overlay="true"><div class="inner-wrap using-image"><div data-bg="https://cdn-blogs.unibet.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/44/2023/08/3487968937.jpg" class="row-bg using-image using-bg-color rocket-lazyload"  style=" background-position: center center; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-color: #d1d1ca; "></div></div><div class="row-bg-overlay" style="background-color:#0a0a0a;  opacity: 0.5; "></div></div><div class="row_col_wrap_12 col span_12 light left">
	<div  class="vc_col-sm-6 wpb_column column_container vc_column_container col no-extra-padding inherit_tablet inherit_phone "  data-t-w-inherits="default" data-bg-cover="" data-padding-pos="all" data-has-bg-color="false" data-bg-color="" data-bg-opacity="1" data-hover-bg="" data-hover-bg-opacity="1" data-animation="" data-delay="0" >

				<div id="fws_654ab41b1df96" data-midnight="" data-column-margin="default" class="wpb_row vc_row-fluid vc_row inner_row standard_section   "  style="padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; "><div class="row-bg-wrap"> <div class="row-bg" ></div> </div><div class="row_col_wrap_12_inner col span_12  left">
	<div  class="vc_col-sm-12 wpb_column column_container vc_column_container col child_column no-extra-padding inherit_tablet inherit_phone "   data-t-w-inherits="default" data-bg-cover="" data-padding-pos="all" data-has-bg-color="false" data-bg-color="" data-bg-opacity="1" data-hover-bg="" data-hover-bg-opacity="1" data-animation="" data-delay="0">

		<div class="wpb_wrapper">
			
<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " >
	<div class="wpb_wrapper">
		<h2><span style="color: #ffffff">PRO LEAGUE</span></h2>
	</div>
</div>




<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " >
	<div class="wpb_wrapper">
		<p><span style="color: #ffffff">Format, dates, favoris&#8230; : tout ce que vous devez savoir la saison 2023/2024 !</span></p>
	</div>
</div>




		</div> 
	</div>
	</div>

	<div  class="vc_col-sm-6 wpb_column column_container vc_column_container col no-extra-padding inherit_tablet inherit_phone "  data-t-w-inherits="default" data-bg-cover="" data-padding-pos="all" data-has-bg-color="false" data-bg-color="" data-bg-opacity="1" data-hover-bg="" data-hover-bg-opacity="1" data-animation="" data-delay="0" >
		<div class="vc_column-inner" ><div class="column-bg-overlay-wrap" data-bg-animation="none"><div class="column-bg-overlay"></div></div>
			<div class="wpb_wrapper">
				<div id="fws_654ab41b2e343" data-midnight="" data-column-margin="default" class="wpb_row vc_row-fluid vc_row inner_row standard_section   "  style="padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; "><div class="row-bg-wrap"> <div class="row-bg" ></div> </div><div class="row_col_wrap_12_inner col span_12  left">
	<div  class="vc_col-sm-12 wpb_column column_container vc_column_container col child_column no-extra-padding inherit_tablet inherit_phone "   data-t-w-inherits="default" data-bg-cover="" data-padding-pos="all" data-has-bg-color="false" data-bg-color="" data-bg-opacity="1" data-hover-bg="" data-hover-bg-opacity="1" data-animation="" data-delay="0">
		<div class="vc_column-inner" ><div class="column-bg-overlay-wrap" data-bg-animation="none"><div class="column-bg-overlay"></div></div>
		<div class="wpb_wrapper">
			
<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " >
	<div class="wpb_wrapper">
		<h2><span style="color: #ffffff">Nouveau ! Unibet Impact</span></h2>
	</div>
</div>




<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " >
	<div class="wpb_wrapper">
		<p><span style="color: #ffffff">Ensemble pour un jeu responsable, un sport éthique et une pratique sportive solidaire</span></p>
	</div>
</div>




		</div> 
	</div>
	</div> 
</div></div><div id="fws_654ab41b2e614" data-midnight="" data-column-margin="default" class="wpb_row vc_row-fluid vc_row inner_row standard_section   "  style="padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; "><div class="row-bg-wrap"> <div class="row-bg" ></div> </div><div class="row_col_wrap_12_inner col span_12  left">

	<div class="wpb_wrapper">
		<h4 style="text-align: center"><span class="s1">Le Blog Unibet, le repaire des parieurs !</span></h4>
<p class="p1" style="text-align: center"><span class="s1">Bienvenue sur le blog Unibet Sports. Retrouvez les dernières actualités de vos sports préférés : football, tennis, basket-ball et plus encore. Découvrez l&rsquo;opinion tranchée de nos Experts sur les compétitions et matchs à venir, et profitez des meilleurs conseils pour vos paris. Apprenez-en davantage sur vos équipes préférées ou lancez-vous à la découverte de nouvelles disciplines, comme l&rsquo;Esports. Quoi que vous cherchiez, vous le trouverez ici sur le blog Unibet Sports.</span></p>

<script>window.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
    jQuery("ul.navigation-panel li a").click(function () {
        if (jQuery(".MobileLeftNavigation__root___1ERdQ").hasClass('MobileLeftNavigation__show___121vM')) {
            jQuery(".MobileLeftNavigation__root___1ERdQ").removeClass('MobileLeftNavigation__show___121vM');
            jQuery(".MobileLeftNavigation__root___1ERdQ").addClass('MobileLeftNavigation__hide___121vM');
        } else {
            jQuery(".MobileLeftNavigation__root___1ERdQ").addClass('MobileLeftNavigation__show___121vM');
            jQuery(".MobileLeftNavigation__root___1ERdQ").removeClass('MobileLeftNavigation__hide___121vM');
        }
    });
    jQuery(".MenuHeader__icon___3IN7p").click(function () {
        jQuery(".MobileLeftNavigation__show___121vM").addClass('MobileLeftNavigation__hide___121vM');
        jQuery(".MobileLeftNavigation__show___121vM").removeClass('MobileLeftNavigation__show___121vM');
    });
    jQuery("#mobCatMenuIcon").click(function () {
        jQuery(".MobileRightNav").addClass('menu-open');
        jQuery(".MobileRightNav").removeClass('menu-closed');
    });
    jQuery(".MobileRightNav #ocnBack").click(function () {
        jQuery(".MobileRightNav").removeClass('menu-open');
        jQuery(".MobileRightNav").addClass('menu-closed');
    });
});</script>
